<cl=A2A2A2>

The guild of Armorers was established by the best craftsmen in the Sphere and keeps its secrets very well. Magicians who have gained any noticeable degree will not be admitted to the Guild. They do not practice magic here, or martial arts, so their knowledge of elements and battle skills leave much to be desired. Armorers cannot be called unprotected though, as the secret knowledge of their guild provide them with very powerful protection from military and particularly magical attacks. Besides, forging weapons does play a part, so an experienced armorer can stop any enemy with a blow, even without a weapon. Armorers prefer to avoid fighting though, pursuing their favorite pastime. Their art is highly appreciated in entire Sphere and even the guild of Sorcerers refuses to work with weapons that is not branded by Armorers.
<br>
<br><tab><l="hts:\\language\guilds.hts">See guild descriptions<\l><br>
